<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Negotix</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/about.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Top Navigation Bar -->
    <%- include('./partials/header') %>

    <div class="background-shapes">
        <div class="shape shape-1"></div>
        <div class="shape shape-2"></div>
        <div class="shape shape-3"></div>
        <div class="shape shape-4"></div>
        <div class="shape shape-5"></div>
        <div class="shape shape-6"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="main-content">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        
        <div class="about-container">
            <div class="about-left">
                <div class="about-mission">
                    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                    <p>At Negotix, we're on a mission to revolutionize how people negotiate and trade goods online. We believe in creating a transparent, fair, and efficient marketplace where buyers and sellers can connect directly and negotiate the best deals.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="about-right">
                <div class="about-section">
                    <h2>Who We Are</h2>
                    <p>Negotix was founded in 2025 by a team of e-commerce enthusiasts who saw a gap in the market for a platform that empowers users to negotiate prices directly. Our diverse team brings together expertise in technology, retail, and customer experience.</p>
                    <p>We're a company that values innovation, transparency, and putting our users first in everything we do.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="about-section">
                    <h2>What We Do</h2>
                    <p>Our platform connects buyers with sellers in a unique environment where price negotiation is not just possibleâ€”it's encouraged. We provide the tools and security to make online negotiations simple, safe, and satisfying for everyone involved.</p>
                    <ul class="feature-list">
                        <li>Direct buyer-seller negotiations</li>
                        <li>Secure payment processing</li>
                        <li>Verified user profiles</li>
                        <li>Dispute resolution services</li>
                        <li>Community marketplace</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="about-section">
                    <h2>Our Values</h2>
                    <div class="values-grid">
                        <div class="value-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-handshake"></i>
                            <h3>Trust</h3>
                            <p>Building a marketplace where users can trust each other and our platform.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="value-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
                            <h3>Innovation</h3>
                            <p>Constantly improving our platform with new features and technologies.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="value-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                            <h3>Community</h3>
                            <p>Fostering a vibrant community of buyers and sellers who help each other.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="value-item">
                            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                            <h3>Security</h3>
                            <p>Protecting our users' data and transactions with state-of-the-art security.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="about-section">
                    <h2>How Negotix Works</h2>
                    <ol class="process-list">
                        <li>
                            <span class="process-number">1</span>
                            <div class="process-content">
                                <h3>List or Browse</h3>
                                <p>Sellers list their products or buyers browse available listings to find what they need.</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <span class="process-number">2</span>
                            <div class="process-content">
                                <h3>Negotiate</h3>
                                <p>Use our negotiation tools to discuss price, delivery options, and other terms directly.</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <span class="process-number">3</span>
                            <div class="process-content">
                                <h3>Secure Payment</h3>
                                <p>Once terms are agreed, payment is processed through our secure payment system.</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <span class="process-number">4</span>
                            <div class="process-content">
                                <h3>Delivery & Feedback</h3>
                                <p>The product is delivered, and both parties can leave feedback to build their reputation.</p>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="platform-section">
            <h2>Our Platform Benefits</h2>
            <div class="benefits-grid">
                <div class="benefit-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-percentage"></i>
                    <h3>Better Deals</h3>
                    <p>Get the best possible price through direct negotiation without middlemen.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="benefit-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-lock"></i>
                    <h3>Secure Transactions</h3>
                    <p>Our escrow system ensures both buyers and sellers are protected.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="benefit-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-comments"></i>
                    <h3>Direct Communication</h3>
                    <p>Chat directly with the other party to clarify details and build trust.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="benefit-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                    <h3>Reputation System</h3>
                    <p>Our rating system helps you identify reliable trading partners.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <%- include('./partials/footer') %>

    <a href="#" class="back-to-top" id="backToTop">
        <i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i>
    </a>

    <canvas id="particles"></canvas>



    <script src="/js/about.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
